Piano App
The keys of the piano will have the corresponding notes' name on them. 
The colors of the keys will be the same as a normal piano.
When the user presses down on a key, it will play the corresponding note/frequency. 
The user will be able to press down on multiple keys at the same time. 
The app will be named Le Piano.
The app wil be free and it will be usuable offline. 
The piano will have 4 octaves which is wquivalent to 32 keys
The app will be avaible for PC and mobile devices
